{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I heard the music, and I froze.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing came out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't have to pretend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Believe me, I didn't have to pretend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I did nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The music started playing and started playing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then one of them called out to me-- it was like a freak show.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Dance!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Dance for us!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I started dancing-- I had choreographed something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No idea what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, totally irrational, totally stupid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The only thing I remember, I ended up in a split, which was the only thing I had choreographed, anyway.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then stayed down, until Meier came and took me off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, it is true, they never asked me again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "However, they really thought I did it on purpose, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and took away my E4 number, decision, and gave me a transport number.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, I have no proof that this was in conjunction, this one followed because of the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But there was no other reason for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then it happened that the camp was full, and full, and fuller.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And rumor started to spread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Rumor started to spread that there were people among who had always escaped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was a certain spot in Belgium where the train was going very slowly, uphill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this was a spot where you could jump, disappear into the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Underground was notified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were there waiting for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It seems that these transport from Mechelen, wherever their destination was, there was always much less arrived than had left Mechelen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And after many, many, many, many months of this, it seems that Berlin started very worried about it, or angry about it, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they ordered, first of all, that the camp-- which had never happened before-- has to be emptied out completely.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Everybody leaves.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
